Package: Rflow
Title: MCP Server and R Toolkit for Claude Code
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Carly", "Chery", email = "cchery@earth.ac.cr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that gives Claude Code
    direct access to R. Exposes 16 tools covering R code execution, file
    analysis, file system operations, R internals search, Random Forest
    machine learning, and workspace management. No API key required —
    works with any Claude Code plan including Max subscriptions.
